data.description:
FREEEEEEE Rent until 1-1-24 with lease agrement. 3 Month, 6 Month or 12 Month Lease terms (Valid from 12/16/2023 till 12/31/2023)

ALERT ALERT ALERT
 

Cooper School District! Beautiful 3-2-2 in beautiful Bell Farms. If you are looking for a great rental and deal direct with the owner, this is your chance! Upgraded Maytag appliances! Reverse Osmosis water, Ceramic Wood look tile, Corner Fireplace, Soaker Garden Tub and Seperate Shower in Master Bath, Split Bedrooms and Large Master closet that is accessable to laundry room! Outside pets only 20lbs or smaller. No Smoking!! (strictly enforced). HURRY and call before this one is gone!

Tenant responsible for all utilities and yard maintenance. If yard is not maintained, owner will bill tenant for yard maintenance up to $100 per mowing.
